4792,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔識野, 果度有條友講果5000萬係離職補償金既話, 係唔使比入息稅, 堅定流??</blockquote><br />\n你打去IRD問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f08ba7288eeeb9bb9d34cb0a5cc2976321c292f","tid":254792,"uid":63287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:11:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我唔識野, 果度有條友講果5000萬係離職補償金既話, 係唔使比入息稅, 堅定流??</blockquote><br />\n你打去IRD問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梁生係UGL離職？"},{"pid":"98ece49d62db4db87bbf95a62dc8ff466fa9efbb","tid":254792,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:12:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/taxes/salaries/salariestax/chargeable/termination.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Ftaxes%2Fsalaries%2Fsalariestax%2Fchargeable%2Ftermination.htm&d=CUR0kzXGIm1HC%2F%2BZBX5zt9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=326e7db9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/taxes/salaries/salariestax/chargeable/termination.htm</a>"},{"pid":"33e13bade36dc3efd10709c1a5f6267eef14628e","tid":254792,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef354fb32094608e7595cf5b2ecb375749097f97","tid":254792,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:17:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a18bbfbd0c2175c631ab625aaa3131896cb857f5","tid":254792,"uid":2839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:19:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我唔識野, 果度有條友講果5000萬係離職補償金既話, 係唔使比入息稅, 堅定流??</blockquote><br />\n你打去IRD問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一般純離職協議既話好似係<br />\n但呢份合約入面有條寫到話要689支持UGL協助收購戴德梁行<br />\n仲要係收購成功後，係UGL合理要求下<br />\n幫手推廣UGL同戴德梁行<br />\n份約有涉及到服務，就算結果係689冇提供到任何服務都好都唔重要<br />\n因為你份約係應承左人，而呢樣野係反映左係合同價值入面<br />\n照計就應該要交入息稅<br />\n<br />\nBTW，就算唔駛交，佢冇申報去行會已經夠死</blockquote><br />\n明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff93b35b05dc3a9ebef25c5f1a1357817c2ccff","tid":254792,"uid":114193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:21:31.000Z","msg":"見隻 68狗 呢幾日係咁吠<br />\n<br />\n就知佢真係好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97daf5b28e47490e95271c0e9da5181ec3eb6efd","tid":254792,"uid":19654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條友真係有料到 識佢真人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n達明喺法律界好有地位其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幸做過佢學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69dfa5c1360334daa53eff6a3a10c26d087836e3","tid":254792,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解馮煒光會畀佢入到嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n白宮發言人搵緊工唔得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7295e0fdacd4d25b614dbc43affb10a4ba8e428","tid":254792,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:39:20.000Z","msg":"689幾時會告佢呢？"},{"pid":"9018d1f98bfae7f57d03998ca37a03473d996ae2","tid":254792,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:46:07.000Z","msg":"佢講一講明白689衰乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfb46f0cbc574f6f9015bd1c721003f624dc66e","tid":254792,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:52:09.000Z","msg":"答yes or no都仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62880e4